"{\"uid\": \"nbcsports.com-pressbox-press-releases-mike-tirico-rebecca-lowe-craig-melvin-ahmed-fareed-and-damon-hack-to-host-nbc-daytime-coverage-of-the-olympic-games-paris-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Primetime Host Mike Tirico also Anchors Afternoon ET NBC Show Live Across the Country    Lowe and Melvin to Host on NBC in Morning and Early Afternoon ET    Fareed Hosts Late Afternoon ET on NBC & Reports Live from around Paris in Morning/Afternoon ET Show    Hack Hosts Late Afternoon PT NBC West Coast Show    NBC to Provide at Least 9 Hours of Daytime Coverage July 27-August 11; All Linear Coverage to Be Streamed on Peacock    Opening Ceremony of the Paris Olympics is Friday, July 26 on NBC, Peacock and Telemundo  STAMFORD, Conn. - May 15, 2024 -Mike Tirico, Rebecca Lowe,Craig Melvin,Ahmed Fareed, andDamon Hacktoday were announced as NBC daytime hosts for the Olympic Games Paris 2024 this summer.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 706, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 26, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tirico\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mike Tirico\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tirico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tirico\"}, {\"begin\": 116, \"end\": 119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9986796152334732, \"rank\": 0.0012571074793368356, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 222, \"end\": 227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7277511079891377e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 289, \"end\": 292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9986796152334732, \"rank\": 0.001257107479336