 film, television, and streaming, and bring to life through our theme parks and consumer experiences.\", \"from\": 4204, \"to\": 4379, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We own and operate leading entertainment and news brands, including NBC, NBC News, MSNBC, CNBC, NBC Sports, Telemundo, NBC Local Stations, Bravo, USA Network, and Peacock, our premium ad-supported streaming service.\", \"from\": 4380, \"to\": 4595, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4448, \"end\": 4451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9986796152334732, \"rank\": 0.0012571074793368356, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We produce and distribute premier filmed entertainment and programming through Universal Filmed Entertainment Group and Universal Studio Group, and have world-renowned theme parks and attractions through Universal Destinations & Experiences.\", \"from\": 4596, \"to\": 4837, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4675, \"end\": 4711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Universal_Pictures\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Universal Filmed Entertainment Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Universal_Pictures\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Universal_Pictures\"}, {\"begin\": 4716, \"end\": 4738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal_Television_and_Streaming\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Universal Studio Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal_Television_and_Streaming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal_Television_and_Streaming\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBCUniversal is a subsidiary of Comcast Corporation.\", \"from\": 4838, \"to\": 4890, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4838, \"end\": 4850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resou